{"tid":1916072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国迫害新疆維族國際認證   美大屠殺博物館：構成反人類罪","createTime":"2020-03-08T16:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T10:20:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e69e0780f1c93143c542080567c41d177b8de8","tid":1916072,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"中國近年屢遭披露迫害新疆維吾爾族的黑幕，包括以「再教育」的名義建立集中營，並強迫8萬名維吾爾人在國際企業代工廠勞動；對此，美國大屠殺博物館（United States Holocaust Memorial Museum，USHMM）表示，「中國政府對維吾爾人的迫害構成反人類罪」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《自由亞洲電台》報導，美國大屠殺博物館所屬的西蒙科約特預防滅絕種族中心主任奇科勒（Naomi Kikoler）在5日的講談表示，新疆維吾爾自治區的情況表明，「有理由相信中國應對反人類罪負責」。<br />\n<br />\n奇科勒還引用相關報告指出，中國政府從2017年以來，以「強烈宗教觀點」與「政治不正確」等罪名關押多達180萬維吾爾人，並對維吾爾拘留者進行政治灌輸、酷刑、強迫勞動，有許多人在新疆集中營裡死亡。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦眾議員麥戈文（Jim McGovern）以及參議員魯比歐（Marco Rubio）也有出席講座，兩人現正共同擔任國會及行政當局中國委員會 （Congressional-Executive Commission on China，簡稱CECC）聯合主席，他們曾在先前的年度報告中提出，中國對新疆維吾爾自治區的政策符合「反人類罪」的定義。<br />\n<br />\n世界維吾爾代表大會（World Uyghur Youth Congress）主席多里坤‧艾沙（Dolkun Isa）表示，美國大屠殺博物館的認定具有「歷史意義」。<br />\n<br />\n據資料指出，反人類罪又叫「危害人類罪」，初次適用是在第二次世界大戰後對針戰犯的審判，而在2002年7月1日生效的《國際刑事法院羅馬規約》裡，反人類罪被定義為「針對人性尊嚴極其嚴重的侵犯與凌辱的眾多行為構成的事實，如政府對民眾實施謀殺、種族滅絕、人體試驗、酷刑、強姦、政治性、種族性或宗教性的迫害，以及其他非人道的行為」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3092948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3092948&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=4f7f0e9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3092948&h=76b48b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3092948</a>"},{"pid":"b6d88d571c4797204acb388d56d1b82033384ad1","tid":1916072,"uid":121146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"德國婆表示：唔好咁大聲呀  一陣激嬲中共呀"},{"pid":"0bb126cc92550ac1e107d2fff4bf50601270eb7c","tid":1916072,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"對於攞撚住勁撚多人民幣嘅商家佬嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本都唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b4ddef5b6326976d6282d07dd70fd3e4142850","tid":1916072,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93911f585eb42bcca89373932963ebfb9010edcc","tid":1916072,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942ddf11337812232ff07b91ac05c267c3c958dd","tid":1916072,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:10:40.000Z","msg":"希望快啲有人出兵打柒小支支<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cdc6a16becea1ac82660d6be1e8ca0ce476a05","tid":1916072,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"中共： 吹呀？"},{"pid":"60ea54642f54fdb7286970741df1020eade5c533","tid":1916072,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d88d571c4797204acb388d56d1b82033384ad1","tid":1916072,"uid":121146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"德國婆表示：唔好咁大聲呀  一陣激嬲中共呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:33:28.000Z","msg":"冇計啦，咁多德國既廠喺芝麻國"},{"pid":"cc988aea6c0013b9dcaf4af825e6593b10be68a8","tid":1916072,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《國際刑事法院羅馬規約》裡，反人類罪被定義為「針對人性尊嚴極其嚴重的侵犯與凌辱的眾多行為構成的事實，如政府對民眾實施謀殺</span></strong><b